@baseUrl = http://localhost:5136
@contentType = application/json
@sampleId = 3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

### ==========================================
### BOOK APIS
### ==========================================

### Obtener lista de libros (con filtros opcionales)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?Filter=Clean&SkipCount=0&MaxResultCount=10&Sorting=title
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Crear un nuevo libro
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "El resplandor",
  "author": "Stephen King",
  "publishDate": "2026-07-13T12:00:00Z"
}

### Obtener un libro por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/{{sampleId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Actualizar un libro por ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/books/{{sampleId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "El resplandor (Edición Especial)",
  "author": "Stephen King",
  "publishDate": "2026-07-13T12:00:00Z"
}

### Eliminar un libro por ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/books/{{sampleId}}

### Buscar libros por autor
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/by-author?author=Stephen%20King
Accept: {{contentType}}


### ==========================================
### CATEGORY APIS
### ==========================================

### Obtener lista de categorías
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories?SkipCount=0&MaxResultCount=10&Sorting=name
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Obtener una categoría por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{sampleId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}


### ==========================================
### STUDENT APIS
### ==========================================
# Nota: Según tu OpenAPI, los endpoints de Student usan los mismos DTOs 
# y estructuras de datos que Book.

### Obtener lista de estudiantes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student?SkipCount=0&MaxResultCount=10
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Crear un estudiante (usa la estructura BookDto)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/student
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Nombre del Estudiante",
  "author": "Carrera / Información",
  "publishDate": "2026-07-13T12:00:00Z"
}

### Obtener un estudiante por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/{{sampleId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Actualizar un estudiante por ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/student/{{sampleId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Nombre Actualizado",
  "author": "Carrera Modificada",
  "publishDate": "2026-07-13T12:00:00Z"
}

### Eliminar un estudiante por ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/student/{{sampleId}}


### ==========================================
### TODO APIS
### ==========================================

### Obtener lista de Todos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos?SkipCount=0&MaxResultCount=10
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Crear un nuevo Todo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Terminar la documentación de la API",
  "isCompleted": false
}

### Obtener un Todo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/{{sampleId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Actualizar un Todo por ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/{{sampleId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Terminar la documentación de la API",
  "isCompleted": true
}

### Eliminar un Todo por ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/{{sampleId}}